Enhancement: Adds progress details while restoring

The command restic restore now shows a progress report while it's restoring files.

Example: [0:42]  23 / 3456 Files,  12.98 MiB / 23.54 GiB,  5.76 %   

Fixes issue: https://github.com/restic/restic/issues/3627

Mentioned in Forum Thread https://forum.restic.net/t/progress-bar-for-restore/5210

https://github.com/restic/restic/pull/3991
